{"tid":2192123,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"為何被野狗追要盯著牠看？內行「一句話」揭犬類本能","createTime":"2020-09-07T02:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T02:29:04.000Z","uid":289214,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ddbba2c17383e4b9d555cc1d025550ff846ac471","tid":2192123,"uid":289214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:26:42.000Z","msg":"說「狗」是人類最忠心的朋友，不過有些路邊的野狗卻會令人生畏。日前有網友就在PTT透露，自己騎車時經過一條小巷子，巷內有不少野狗，其中一隻原本準備衝向他，但他回頭盯著牠看，狗便不再追了，這讓他不禁好奇提問「為什盯著野狗看他就不會再追你了？」問題釣出行家揭密<span class=\"red\">「犬類本能」</span>，直指<span class=\"red\">「你跑你就是獵物」，因為狗有追逃跑獵物的習慣</span>，眼神對上，反而等於是正面對峙，而人的體積比狗大，因此威脅其實不小。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E8%A2%AB%E9%87%8E%E7%8B%97%E8%BF%BD%E8%A6%81%E7%9B%AF%E8%91%97%E7%89%A0%E7%9C%8B-%E5%85%A7%E8%A1%8C-%E5%8F%A5%E8%A9%B1-%E6%8F%AD%E7%8A%AC%E9%A1%9E%E6%9C%AC%E8%83%BD-001442641.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%2587%258E%25E7%258B%2597%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%259B%25AF%25E8%2591%2597%25E7%2589%25A0%25E7%259C%258B-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E5%258F%25A5%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%258A%25AC%25E9%25A1%259E%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%2583%25BD-001442641.html&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=2d5cb90f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E8%A2%AB%E9%87%8E%E7%8B%97%E8%BF%BD%E8%A6%81%E7%9B%AF%E8%91%97%E7%89%A0%E7%9C%8B-%E5%85%A7%E8%A1%8C-%E5%8F%A5%E8%A9%B1-%E6%8F%AD%E7%8A%AC%E9%A1%9E%E6%9C%AC%E8%83%BD-001442641.html</a>"},{"pid":"23373adc9df1b9fd01f3e7ce2344c0a30c1ed4b5","tid":2192123,"uid":279981,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:29:04.000Z","msg":"香港一堆人型犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}